   </div>
</section>
<section id="services">
   <div class="container">
      <h2>Our services</h2>
      <ul class="gallery2">
         <li>
            <%= image_tag "icon1.svg", :alt => "Professional Approach" %>
            <h3>Product Development</h3>
            <p>We can help you tackle any project, big or small.
            Our expertise is in mobile and web development, but
            we also provide backend development, design and
            branding, integrations, and more.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <%= image_tag "icon2.svg", :alt => "Responsive Design" %>
            <h3>Responsive design</h3>
            <p>We are experts in creating responsive web
            applications that look great on any device - from
            laptops to tablets to mobile phones. Our team is
            always on the cutting edge with new technology.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <%= image_tag "icon3.svg", :alt => "Award winning work" %>
            <h3>World Class Service</h3>
            <p>Our products have been finalists in tech competitions and
            accepted into top incubator programs. We treat every project
            as if we were an extension of your team; we only succeed if you do.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <%= image_tag "icon4.svg", :alt => "Website optimization" %>
            <h3>Website optimization</h3>
            <p>We have years of experience in website optimization;
             including user interface re-design, user experience
             consulting, search engine optimization, and search
             engine marketing.</p>
         </li>
      </ul>
   </div> <!-- end container -->
</section>
